@startuml Seq-01 View Availability and List Spots

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 5
skinparam sequenceParticipant underline

actor       "Driver"          as Driver
participant "API Gateway"     as GW
participant "Search Service"  as Search
database    "PostgreSQL"      as DB

== View Availability (Summary) ==

Driver -> GW : GET /availability?vehicle_type=CAR
GW -> Search : GetAvailability(vehicle_type=CAR)
Search -> DB : SELECT floor_number, COUNT(*)\nFROM spots\nWHERE status=AVAILABLE\nAND vehicle_type=CAR\nGROUP BY floor_number
DB --> Search : available count per floor
Search --> GW : GetAvailabilityResponse\n{ total_available=23,\n  floors=[{floor=1, available=5},\n          {floor=2, available=8}, ...] }
GW --> Driver : 200 OK { total_available, floors[] }

note over Driver : Driver sees "23 car spots available"\nand picks Floor 2 to browse

== List Spots (Spot Picker for User-Selected Mode) ==

Driver -> GW : GET /spots?floor_number=2&vehicle_type=CAR
GW -> Search : ListSpots(floor_number=2, vehicle_type=CAR)
Search -> DB : SELECT id, floor_number, spot_code,\n       vehicle_type, status\nFROM spots\nWHERE floor_number=2\nAND vehicle_type=CAR
DB --> Search : individual spot rows
Search --> GW : ListSpotsResponse\n{ spots=[{spot_id=12, spot_code=A1, status=AVAILABLE},\n         {spot_id=13, spot_code=A2, status=LOCKED},\n         {spot_id=14, spot_code=A3, status=AVAILABLE}, ...] }
GW --> Driver : 200 OK { spots[] }

note over Driver : Driver sees floor map with spot statuses\nand selects spot A3 (spot_id=14)\n→ proceeds to CreateReservation (USER_SELECTED)

@enduml
